"Okay, I see you. I see all of y'all. And I got something for you right now. ${b} is coming to the main stage — and if you're not paying attention, that's on you. The lovely ${b}."
"All eyes front — and I mean all of them. ${b} is heading your way. I don't care what you were doing, what you were thinking — none of that matters in about three seconds. ${b}."
"Gentlemen, the energy in this room is about to level up. And the reason? ${b} on the main stage. Get up close and stay there. ${b}."
"I've been watching this room all night... and I know exactly what y'all need. ${b} is on her way out, and she's bringing exactly that. Main stage — ${b}."
"Some of y'all in the back been acting like you're not here for this. I see you. And guess what — ${b} sees you too. She's heading to the main stage. Come on up front. The beautiful ${b}."
"This next one... she's about to make every head turn in this place. ${b} is coming to the main stage. Trust me, you don't want to be looking at your phone right now. ${b}."
"Y'all have been warming up all night. Now let's turn it all the way up. ${b} is heading to the main stage and she's got that thing — you know what I'm talking about. Watch her work. ${b}."
"I need everybody's attention. Not some of it — all of it. ${b} is heading to the stage and she commands a full room. Eyes up, boys. Here she comes... ${b}."
"Fellas, I'm gonna let you in on something. Whatever you thought tonight was gonna be — it just changed. ${b} is coming to the main stage. The gorgeous ${b}."
