"There's a reason ${b} is on this stage. She's the best at what she does and she knows it — and tonight, she's about to prove it. Main stage — the beautiful ${b}."
"${b} is about to walk out here and remind every single one of you why you came. She's that kind of performer. Watch this... ${b}."
"Every time she steps on this stage she does it better than before. ${b} is heading your way, and gentlemen — she is in a league of her own. ${b}."
"Right about now... main stage. ${b}. She's got it — all of it. The look, the moves, the energy. Everything. Here she comes."
